OL,3,CMan accused of brutal rape asked to
OL,4,Cexplain DNA being found on victim
OL,6,FA man accused of a brutal rape for
OL,7,Fwhich another man spent 17 years in
OL,8,Fprison has said his promiscuous
OL,9,Flifestyle could explain his DNA being
OL,10,Ffound on the victim.
OL,12,FPaul Quinn was confronted with DNA
OL,13,Fevidence on the victim's vest top
OL,14,Fwhich had a "billion to one" chance of
OL,15,Fnot matching his own DNA.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
