PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773918340
OL,3,CMan accused of brutal rape asked to
OL,4,Cexplain DNA being found on victim
OL,6,FThe 51-year-old is accused of raping a
OL,7,Fwoman in Little Hulton in Salford in
OL,8,F2003, a crime for which another man -
OL,9,FAndrew Malkinson - was wrongly
OL,10,Fconvicted leading to him spending 17
OL,11,Fyears in prison.
OL,13,FAfter Mr Malkinsons conviction was
OL,14,Foverturned, police arrested Quinn in
OL,15,F2022 after his DNA was found to match
OL,16,Fa sample found on the victims clothing.
OL,18,FDuring his trial at Manchester Crown
OL,19,FCourt, the jury heard audio of his
OL,20,Fpolice interview.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
