OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773918340
OL,3,CMan accused of brutal rape asked to
OL,4,Cexplain DNA being found on victim
OL,6,FIn the recording, a detective asks:
OL,7,F"So how has your DNA, which is one in
OL,8,Fone billion, ended up on her top?"
OL,10,FQuinn replied: "I don't know. I did
OL,11,Fnot do this offence,"
OL,13,FJurors have heard that Quinn claims he
OL,14,Fhad casual sex with up to 2,700 women
OL,15,Fduring his youth, which may explain
OL,16,Fhow his DNA ended up on the victims
OL,17,Fclothing.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@bO]rD@POUsD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
