PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773918340
OL,3,CMan accused of brutal rape asked to
OL,4,Cexplain DNA being found on victim
OL,6,FThe officer said: "You are trying to
OL,7,Fexplain away the DNA, by making out
OL,8,Fyou have slept with the majority of
OL,9,FManchester, over a 16-year period."
OL,11,FQuinn replies: "It could've been from
OL,12,Fcontact with her.
OL,14,F"I have not beat her, I have not raped
OL,15,Fher. If I had done it, I would've told
OL,16,Fyou because I would've been ashamed,
OL,17,Fbut I haven't done it."
OL,26,@nD@SOUqD@cO]sD@POUvD@AOUyD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
