FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773918340
OL,3,CMan accused of brutal rape asked to
OL,4,Cexplain DNA being found on victim
OL,6,FQuinn, aged 29 at the time of the
OL,7,Fattack, was only linked to the crime
OL,8,Fyears later, after scientific advances
OL,9,Fin testing DNA samples.
OL,11,FQuinn told the officers, for around 16
OL,12,Fyears, from the age of 18, he had a
OL,13,Fparty lifestyle at the weekends and
OL,14,Fwould go out with friends and family,
OL,15,Ftake ecstasy pills and other drugs and
OL,16,Fsleep with two or three women each
OL,17,Fweekend.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
