PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773918340
OL,3,CMan accused of brutal rape asked to
OL,4,Cexplain DNA being found on victim
OL,6,FHe said he was married in 1996 and had
OL,7,Ftwo children living at home at the
OL,8,Ftime of the offence, but added: "I
OL,9,Fadmit, I have cheated on my wife
OL,10,Fhundreds of times.
OL,12,F"We have met girls everywhere, it was
OL,13,Fjust the lifestyle we were leading at
OL,14,Fthe time."
OL,16,FHe also said he met some women through
OL,17,Fhis job working for a landscape fence
OL,18,Fbuilding company, though he would
OL,19,Fnever use a protection while having
OL,20,Fsex with random women.
OL,26,@pD@aOUtD@AOUvD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
