PN,39507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773918340
OL,3,CMan accused of brutal rape asked to
OL,4,Cexplain DNA being found on victim
OL,6,FEarlier, the court heard Quinn's ex-
OL,7,Fwife, Catherine Quinn, divorced from
OL,8,Fhim in 2016, said her then-husband
OL,9,Fcame home without his shirt on the
OL,10,Fnight of the rape, July 19, 2003.
OL,12,FShe told the jury she told him she
OL,13,Fhoped the shirt would not be found
OL,14,Fnear the scene of the crime, less than
OL,15,Fa mile from where they lived in Little
OL,16,FHulton.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
