PN,39508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773918340
OL,3,CMan accused of brutal rape asked to
OL,4,Cexplain DNA being found on victim
OL,6,FThe rape victim, a woman in her 30s,
OL,7,Fhad been dragged from the street
OL,8,Fbeside a motorway embankment, brutally
OL,9,Fbeaten, with a nipple almost severed
OL,10,Fand her cheekbone fractured and
OL,11,Fstrangled unconscious before being
OL,12,Fraped twice.
OL,14,FDays after, local shopping centre
OL,15,Fsecurity guard Andrew Malkinson was
OL,16,Fwrongly picked out by two witnesses at
OL,17,Fan identity parade.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
