FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773918340
OL,3,CMan accused of brutal rape asked to
OL,4,Cexplain DNA being found on victim
OL,6,FHe became "the victim of a most
OL,7,Fterrible miscarriage of justice"
OL,8,Fjurors heard, before new DNA evidence
OL,9,Flinked father-of-five Quinn to the
OL,10,Fattack, which he denies.
OL,12,FMr Malkinson made multiple appeals for
OL,13,Fauthorities to review his case before
OL,14,Fhis final attempt led to his appeal
OL,15,Fagainst his conviction being granted
OL,16,Fby the Court of Appeal.
OL,18,FMr Malkinson, now aged 60, and
OL,19,Foriginally from Grimsby, Lincolnshire,
OL,20,Fwas released from jail in 2020.
OL,26,@nD@KOUoD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
