PN,39510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773918340
OL,3,CMan accused of brutal rape asked to
OL,4,Cexplain DNA being found on victim
OL,6,FQuinn, who moved to Exeter, Devon in
OL,7,F2017, has pleaded not guilty to two
OL,8,Fcounts of rape, grievous bodily harm
OL,9,Fand attempting to choke or strangle
OL,10,Fhis victim to render her unconscious
OL,11,Fwhile he carried out the attack.
OL,13,FThe trial was adjourned.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
